OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781111161
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to rule out tax hikes
OL,4,Cto fund defence spending
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Frefused to rule out tax hikes to fund
OL,8,Fdefence spending.
OL,10,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,11,Fraised the issue at Prime Minister's
OL,12,FQuestions, asking whether taxpayers
OL,13,Fshould expect an increase, and Starmer
OL,14,Fdeclined to respond directly.
OL,16,FThe government's defence investment
OL,17,Fplan is due to be published ahead of
OL,18,Fthe Nato summit in Turkey, which
OL,19,Fbegins on July 7.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
