CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781111161
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to rule out tax hikes
OL,4,Cto fund defence spending
OL,6,FIt was originally planned for
OL,7,Fpublication last autumn but has been
OL,8,Frepeatedly delayed.
OL,10,FIn the Commons, Badenoch said, "There
OL,11,Fis still no defence investment plan."
OL,13,FShe suggested the delay was due to Sir
OL,14,FKeir Starmer not knowing "where the
OL,15,Fmoney is coming from" and said, "the
OL,16,Fmilitary is waiting".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781111161
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to rule out tax hikes
OL,4,Cto fund defence spending
OL,6,FThe opposition leader then went on to
OL,7,Fsay that the government has three
OL,8,Foptions: "cutting spending, more
OL,9,Fborrowing, or higher taxes", and asked
OL,10,Fwhether Starmer would "rule out
OL,11,Fraising taxes".
OL,13,FThe PM pointed to the Conservatives'
OL,14,Frecord in office, accusing them of
OL,15,Fdamaging the armed forces.
OL,17,FHe added: "When they left office, 47
OL,18,Fout of 49 major defence contracts were
OL,19,Fdelayed or over budget.
OL,26,@sD@NO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781111161
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to rule out tax hikes
OL,4,Cto fund defence spending
OL,6,F"That is what we are fixing. You can't
OL,7,Fjust scrub away and forget".
OL,9,FHe continued by pointing to Labour's
OL,10,Fincrease in defence spending and said
OL,11,Fthat the defence investment plan will
OL,12,Fbe published "before the Nato summit
OL,13,Fcoming up in just a few weeks' time".
OL,15,FBadenoch then said, "I asked him if he
OL,16,Fwould rule out tax rises.
OL,18,F"He did not rule out raising taxes, so
OL,19,Ftax rises are coming."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@UOUzD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
