CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781111161
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to rule out tax hikes
OL,4,Cto fund defence spending
OL,6,FThis all comes amid reports of a
OL,7,Fdispute at the heart of government
OL,8,Fover the investment plan, known as Dip.
OL,10,FStarmer and Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,11,Fare reportedly arguing for a #15
OL,12,Fbillion package, far less than the #28
OL,13,Fbillion which defence officials have
OL,14,Fcalled for.
OL,16,FBadenoch accused the PM of
OL,17,Foverspending in the last two budgets
OL,18,Fand said that the cost of benefits "is
OL,19,Fset to rise to over #200 billion by
OL,20,Fthe end of the decade".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
