OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781111161
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to rule out tax hikes
OL,4,Cto fund defence spending
OL,6,FShe said that the PM "has things the
OL,7,Fwrong way" and called for him to cut
OL,8,Fwelfare to fund defence.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIn response, Starmer said: "We are not
OL,16,Fgoing to take lectures on defence from
OL,17,Fthe party opposite after what they did
OL,18,Fto the armed forces, and nor are we
OL,19,Fgoing to take lectures on the economy,
OL,20,Fwhich they crashed and we had to pick
OL,21,Fup."
OL,26,@wD@\OU}D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
