OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781111161
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to rule out tax hikes
OL,4,Cto fund defence spending
OL,6,FSpeaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle warned
OL,7,Fministers against publishing on
OL,8,FFriday, telling the Commons it would
OL,9,Fbe a "kick in the face" and accused
OL,10,Fthe government of treating
OL,11,Fparliamentarians as "second-class
OL,12,Fcitizens".
